Package: Texevier
Type: Package
Title: Template for Formal Research Papers with the Elsevier Latex Format
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Nico", "Katzke", email = "nfkatzke@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Nico Katzke <nfkatzke@gmail.com>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.1)
Imports:
	tidyverse,
    ggplot2,
    rmarkdown,
    utils,
    knitr,
    xtable,
    huxtable,
    ggthemes,
  	devtools
Suggests:
  	xts
Description: Provides users with a quick means of setting up
    the standard accepted academic paper layout in the 'Elsevier' format. Users will have to have
    'Latex' installed first, as well as 'rmarkdown' and 'Rstudio'. This package
	creates an easily usable template for doing formal write-ups in the 'Elsevier' format.
